<h1><a href="/">Home</a></h1>
<h1>Update {{user.fname}} {{user.lname}}:</h1>
<form id="updateuser" action="/user" method="post">
    First name: <input id="fname" type="text" name="fname" value="{{user.fname}}" required /><br>
    Last name: <input id="lname" type="text" name="lname" value="{{user.lname}}" required /><br>
    Email: <input id="email" type="email" name="email" value="{{user.email}}" required /><br>
    Address Line 1: <input id="add_line1" type="text" name="add_line1" value="{{user.add_line1}}" required /><br>
    Address Line 2: <input id="add_line2" type="text" name="add_line2" value="{{user.add_line2}}" /><br>
    City: <input id="city" type="text" name="city" value="{{user.city}}" required /><br>
    State: <input id="state" type="text" name="add_state" value="{{user.add_state}}" maxlength="2" required /><br>
    Zip: <input id="zip" type="text" name="zip" value="{{user.zip}}" minlength="5" maxlength="5" required /><br>
	Shop Name: {{user.shop_name}}<br>
</form>
<button onclick="updateUser({{user.uid}})">Update</button><button type="cancel" onclick="javascript:window.location='./';">Cancel</button>
<br>
<p>To add a merchant shop to a User or change the 1-to-1 User-Merchant relationship <br>
go to the <a href="/merchant">Merchants page</a> and create a new Merchant.</p>